<h3>Research &gt; Online Databases A - Z</h3>


<p><em>Online databases are reliable, accurate information sources available   remotely, 24/7 to Warrenville Library cardholders. You will need your   Warrenville library card number and 4 digit pin number to access the databases.</em></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>For a listing of online databases and resources by subject,<a href="onlineresourcesreference.htm"> click here</a>.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><A href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=nbObit" target="_blank"><STRONG>America's Obituary and Death Notices </STRONG></A> &ndash; The largest and most comprehensive collection of newspaper obituaries and death   notices. Search by name, date range, or text.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=ancestry" target="_blank"><STRONG>Ancestry Library Edition</STRONG></A> &ndash; Includes records from the U.S. census (1790 -   1930); military records; court, land and probate records; vital and church   records; directories and more. <STRONG>While the Library is closed, Ancestry is available for remote use.</STRONG>.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=oclcFSartcl" target="_blank"><STRONG>ArticleFirst</STRONG></A> &ndash; Index of articles from the contents   pages of journals. Often provides a list of libraries that own the journal   title.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=atozdb" target="_blank"><strong>AtoZ Databases</strong></a> &ndash; Search businesses, individuals, executives and job listings, or create mailing lists and sales leads.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=autorefctr" target="_blank"><strong>Auto Repair Source</strong></A> &ndash; Factory drawings, step-by-step maintenance instructions, technical service bulletins and recalls, and more. </p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="https://beta-liboff.public-record.com/remote/check" target="_blank"><strong>Check Illinois from Record Information Services</strong></a> &ndash; Search Illinois public records and perform basic background checks. See Record Information Services for more Illinois public records.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=nbCTrib" target="_blank"><strong>Chicago Tribune Historical Archives</strong></A> &ndash; Full-text of historical issues and events from the 1920s to 1984, and obituaries from 1860 to 1984. </p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=crcro" target="_blank"><strong>ConsumerReports.org</strong></A> &ndash; Features ratings and   recommendations on thousands of products and services in categories including   appliances, cars, electronics and computers, home and garden, health and   fitness, babies and kids, food, personal finance, and travel. Free access to   product buying advice, blogs, safety alerts, recalls, a searchable archive of   the past four years of Ratings, <EM>Consumer Reports'</EM> exclusive product-   and car-reliability reports, comprehensive decision guides, access to   consumer/user reviews, and much more. </p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://www.gpo.gov/" target="_blank"><STRONG>GPO</STRONG></A> &ndash; Covers U.S. government documents, including   Congressional reports, hearings, debates, and records; judiciary materials; and   documents issued by executive departments (Defense, State, Labor, and Office of   the President). </p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=HeritageQ" target="_blank"><STRONG>Heritage Quest Online</STRONG></A> &ndash; Resource for census data,   family records and local histories.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=LExpress" target="_blank"><STRONG>LearningExpress</STRONG></A> &ndash; Interactive tutorials and practice   tests to help users improve basic skills in reading, writing, and math, as well   as prepare for high-stakes tests such as the GED, GRE, ACT, and SAT. The   platform can help prepare for a wide range of career-oriented licensing and   certification exams in health care, education, civil service, and homeland   security.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://www.lynda.com/portal/sip?org=warrenville.com" target="_blank"><strong>Lynda.com</strong></A> &ndash;Thousands of video courses in business, technology, and creative skills taught by industry experts. Learn software, design, coding, and business skills at your own pace, prepare for certification exams, and beef up your resume with new skills. This resource is available to Warrenville Public Library District cardholders only. </p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=MFile" target="_blank"><strong>MasterFILE Premiere</strong></a>&ndash; Search full-text articles from magazines like <i>Bon Appetit</i>, <i>GQ</i>, <i>National Geographic</i>, and more.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=Mango" target="_blank"><STRONG>Mango Languages</STRONG></A> &ndash; An online language learning system   teaching practical conversation skills for a wide variety of popular languages.   With everyday dialogue from native speakers, engaging interactive lessons and a   unique intuitive teaching style, Mango increases your ability to use, adapt and   build on what you learn.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=oclcFSmedln" target="_blank"><STRONG>MEDLINE</STRONG></A> &ndash; Abstracts encompassing all areas of   medicine, including dentistry and nursing.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=Mstar" target="_blank"><strong>Morningstar Investment  Research Center</strong></A> &ndash; This  product provides information on stocks and mutual funds for in-depth research  and portfolio construction. It also includes access to Morningstar newsletters  and educational tools.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://www.libraryaware.com/1074/Subscribers/Subscribe" target="_blank"><STRONG>NextReads</STRONG></A> &ndash; Sign up for <EM>NextReads</EM>,    free eMail newsletters of &quot;great reads&quot; for adults, youth and teens. </p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=novelistplus" target="_blank"><STRONG>NovelistPlus</STRONG></A> &ndash; Provides reviews, annotations, and   more for over 150,000 fiction and 50,000 non-fiction titles. Includes author   read-alikes, book discussion guides, book talks, and feature articles. Also   includes tools for school media specialists and teachers. </p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=novelistk8plus" target="_blank"><STRONG>Novelist K-8Plus</STRONG></A> &ndash; Find recommended reads and read-alikes for children and teens.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://beta-liboff.public-record.com/remote" target="_blank"><STRONG>Record Information Services</STRONG></A> &ndash; Scroll through public   records on new homeowners, new businesses, bankruptcies, legal judgements and more for Cook, DuPage, DeKalb, Kane, Kendall, Lake, McHenry and Will counties.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=RefUSA" target="_blank"><STRONG>ReferenceUSA Business</STRONG></A> &ndash; Directory information on USA   businesses, from 1 to more than 10,000 employees. Includes executive names,   company addresses, phone numbers, ticker symbols, websites, headquarters and   more.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=RefUSA" target="_blank"><STRONG>ReferenceUSA Healthcare</STRONG></A> &ndash; National directory of   over 850,000 physicians, surgeons and dentists. Includes state of license,   medical school attended, patients per week, contact info and more. </p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=RefUSA" target="_blank"><STRONG>ReferenceUSA New Business</STRONG></A> &ndash; Directory information on   new USA businesses - 50,000 added weekly. Includes employee size, sales volume,   zipcode, SIC listing and more.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=RefUSA" target="_blank"><STRONG>ReferenceUSA Residential</STRONG></A> &ndash; Directory information on   over 200 million residences. Search by phone number, name or address. </p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=tut" target="_blank"><STRONG>Tutor.com</STRONG></A> &ndash; Tutor.com is a free, on-demand online tutoring service that connects students in   Kindergarten - 12th grade and introductory college students to expert tutors in   math, science, social studies and English via the Internet. The Adult Learner   section supports those earning their GED, seeking grammar help with their resume   and more. Live Homework Help is available every day from 10 a.m. to midnight.&nbsp;   Spanish-speaking tutors are available in math, science, social studies and adult   learning every day from 10 a.m. to midnight.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><A href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=UClass" target="_blank"><STRONG>Universal Class Library Edition</STRONG></A> &ndash; Over 540 courses   offered in Exercise and Fitness, Entrepreneurship, Arts and Music, Home and   Garden Care, Cooking, Computers and Technology, Health and Medicine,   Homeschooling, Job Assistance, Law and Legal, Parenting and Family, Pet and   Animal Care plus much more. With real instructors guiding the learning, engaging   video-based lessons, a collaborative learning environment, graded lesson tests,   certificates of achievement and Continuing Education Units available for   selected courses, students enjoy an engaging and measurable learning experience   that helps them master and document their educational goals.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="https://rpa.warrenville.com/rpa/default/webauth.htm?rs=ValueLine" target="_blank"><Strong>Value Line Research Center</Strong></a> &ndash; <strong> </strong>Access to Value Line's leading publications covering stocks,  mutual funds, options and convertible securities as well as special situation  stocks. Includes customized screening, stock lookup, industry lookup, custom company reports, model portfolios, &ldquo;real-time&rdquo; supplementary analyst reports and more.</p>



